Why Mr. Flamsteed and Mrs. Somerset, how lovely of you to pay me a visit! What do you honor me with your presence for?

FLAMSTEED
(Holds book)
This text. Do you know anything about it?

NEWTON
Why yes, it appears to be a book.

FLAMSTEED
Do you know who made it?

NEWTON
